Firstly install vundel: 
git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle
Then:
git clone https://github.com/liufengxu/vimrc_conf.git ~  
or 
git clone https://github.com/liufengxu/vimrc_conf.git yourdir/
and cp .vimrc and .vimrc.bundle to ~/
Then:
exit vim and open vim again, input:
:BundleInstall
wait for vundle install the plugins
